      <title>清算所发出的追加保证金通知可能会引发未来的危机</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-04/margin-calls-from-clearinghouses-risk-stoking-crises-bis-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[国际清算银行的研究人员表示，持有超过 1 万亿美元流动资产的中央清算所可能会加剧金融压力，造成“利润螺旋”，从而压低资产价格。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-04/margin-calls-from-clearinghouses-risk-stoking-crises-bis-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 04 Dec 2023 12:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
